01:18:25,131 --> 01:18:26,491
In the school year 2013 to 14, we piloted

1107
01:18:28,998 --> 01:18:39,564
a LICE protocol change that focused on keeping students in school if they had presence of NITs, which are LICE eggs.

1108
01:18:40,664 --> 01:18:57,914
